{"about_the_game":"NobodyNowhere is a side-scrolling, story-driven text adventure game in pixel art. The story is set in 2079, when a Replicant awakens in a lab facility amidst a life-or-death situation. The secret replicant aid agency, White Dove, tries to rescue him but fails. In the process they stumble on the real secret of the Replicant project...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/bt1_EN.png?t=1737948309\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/2-2.png?t=1737948309\" /><br>Human Science Research Corp is a research organization dedicated to the study of the human body and individual consciousness. Their research focuses on the emergence of individual human thought and the transfer of consciousness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/bt2EN.png?t=1737948309\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/js1EN.png?t=1737948309\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/js2EN.png?t=1737948309\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/bt3EN.png?t=1737948309\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You play as two different characters and investigate the secrets of Human Science Research Corp.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Detailed pixel animation and fast-paced dialogue create an immersive, animated-movie-like experience.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the world, solve the puzzles with Brain Computer Interface (BCI) and avoid the enemy attacks to find out how the story ends.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Email\uff1a</h2><a href=\"mailto:taghadal@163.com\">taghadal@163.com</a>","background":"https://share